sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Auditor
    participant V as Replay Validator
    participant S as Substrate
    participant E as Evidence Store

    A->>V: Submit Proofpack (Receipts + Payload)
    V->>E: Fetch Original Receipts
    V->>S: Initialize Replay Session
    loop For each recorded Step
        S->>S: Re-execute Payload deterministically
        S->>E: Emit Replayed Receipt
        V->>V: Compare Original vs Replayed
        alt Matches
            V->>V: Mark as Consistent
        else Diverges (Drift)
            V->>V: Record Drift Details
            V->>E: Emit replay_drift Receipt
        end
    end
    V->>E: Emit replay_consistent (if no drift)
    V-->>A: Return ReplayEnvelope (Verification Result)
